361
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:12,210
♪ Just like my lover's red face ♪

362
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:15,980
♪ The tender whisper of the lover ♪

363
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:19,630
♪ is as sweet as sugar ♪

