367
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:31,270
Gulistan, you dance just as well as
she does.

368
00:17:45,270 --> 00:17:46,530
What's wrong with you?

369
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,470
What's up?

370
00:17:50,860 --> 00:17:51,920
What kind of perfume did you buy?

371
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:53,180
The smell is so strong.

372
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,460
Is it strong?

373
00:17:55,810 --> 00:17:57,070
We bought it together.

374
00:17:57,490 --> 00:17:58,570
Minawar.

375
00:17:58,570 --> 00:18:00,700
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

376
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:02,190
I'm fine.

377
00:18:02,210 --> 00:18:03,010
I'm fine.

378
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:04,230
I'm fine.

379
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:36,000
You look like a refugee.

380
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:37,430
I just hope you would

381
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:39,320
let me help you a little.

382
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:40,880
I am really a "refugee."

383
00:18:41,170 --> 00:18:42,950
Everything I owned in Shanghai

384
00:18:43,410 --> 00:18:45,710
is right here. So heavy.

385
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:58,010
Sorry.

386
00:18:58,230 --> 00:18:59,760
This box isn't very sturdy.

387
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:01,070
Sorry.

388
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:06,440
Architectural Design Portfolio.

389
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:14,900
Did you draw this?

390
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:16,840
No, wait.

391
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,890
You majored in architectural design.

392
00:19:18,890 --> 00:19:20,090
How did you end up in real estate sales?

393
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:21,220
And you draw so well.

394
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:23,390
It would be a pity to give it up.

395
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:24,750
Don't act like

396
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,610
you don't know the cost of living.

397
00:19:27,570 --> 00:19:28,970
Right after graduation,

398
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:30,350
it was so hard to find a job.

399
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,660
You know that as well as I do.

400
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:32,400
As for me,

401
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:34,800
I was dead set on buying a house
in Shanghai.

402
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:37,070
I was afraid if I didn't buy one then,

403
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:39,000
I would never be able to afford one.

404
00:19:40,730 --> 00:19:43,490
It's not exactly giving up.

405
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:46,020
The design you just saw

406
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:47,910
was for a part-time job I got online.

407
00:19:47,910 --> 00:19:49,620
Though there weren't many orders,

408
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:51,010
and it didn't pay much.

409
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:54,310
Do you know Metro Line 11 in Shanghai?

410
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,960
Line 11?

411
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:57,430
I know it.

412
00:19:58,860 --> 00:19:59,660
What about it?

413
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,780
The house I bought is right by Line 11.

414
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,900
Isn't that nice?

415
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:06,420
Huaqiao Station, Line 11.

416
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:12,860
I think Jiangsu is pretty good too.

417
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:15,050
Good environment and good value for money.

418
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:16,270
No worse than Shanghai.

419
00:20:16,270 --> 00:20:16,970
Right.

420
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:18,730
I remember

421
00:20:18,990 --> 00:20:21,720
